flowchart TD
  K[Knowledge Article] --> V{visibility}
  V -- public --> VIEW[Anyone with access can view]
  V -- private --> ASSIGN{Assigned?}
  ASSIGN -- User --> U[KnowledgeAssignedUser]
  ASSIGN -- Group --> G[KnowledgeAssignedGroup]
  U & G --> OK[Grant access]
  OK --> EMAIL[KnowledgeEmailLog]
